Class TestKsqlRestApp

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.junit.rules.ExternalResource
      • io.confluent.ksql.rest.server.TestKsqlRestApp
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.junit.rules.TestRule
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TestKsqlRestAppWaitingOnPrecondition

    public class TestKsqlRestApp
extends org.junit.rules.ExternalResource
    Junit external resource for managing an instance of KsqlRestApplication. Generally used in conjunction with EmbeddedSingleNodeKafkaCluster 
    {@code
   private static final EmbeddedSingleNodeKafkaCluster CLUSTER = new EmbeddedSingleNodeKafkaCluster();

   private static final TestKsqlRestApp REST_APP = TestKsqlRestApp
       .builder(CLUSTER::bootstrapServers)
       .build();
